data.description: Lakefront 3 bed/2 bath with loft to serve as extra sleeping, office, or playroom.  Home has been well maintained and ready for your special touches.  Low maintenance exterior and lawn with short, flat distance to water's edge.  Craftroom/workshop with A/C source in garage or remove for extra parking.  Metal roof and covered patio to enjoy the lakeside under shade. Plenty of frontage to add dock. County location perfect for short-term rental program with no permits required.
